<title>BAWI KHRIH LE KHRIHFABU CAAH CH394</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 &quot;Bawi Khrih le Khrihfabu caah,&quot; tiin, Au cio tuah u, kan Siangpahrang
 min thangthat u, Seino thazang in tuan kha i tim u si, Biatak le phung
 ding ca'h fek in dir u si.

[C1]
   Jesuh kan Khamhbawi ca le, A thi in a cawkmi, Amah a Khrihfabu
   ca-ah, Bawipa kan thianter ko.

[V2]
 &quot;Bawi Khrih le Khrihfabu caah,&quot; tiin, Thlacam in nifa kan vailam i put
 u si, Thiang Thlarau thawnnak kha i bochan cio in, Kan caan that bik
 lioah a rian tuan u si.

[C2]
   Jesuh kan Khamhbawi ca le, A thi in a cawkmi, Amah a Khrihfabu
   ca-ah, Bawipa kan thianter ko.

[V3]
 &quot;Bawi Khrih le Khrihfabu caah,&quot; thazang, fimnak, sui le ngun, kan
 chawva le kan caan zong, Amah cu a tha bik kan ngeihmi vialte, Kan
 lungthin tak le dawtnak he pe u si.

[C3]
   Jesuh kan Khamhbawi ca le, A thi in a cawkmi, Amah a Khrihfabu
   ca-ah, Bawipa kan thianter ko.

[V4]
 &quot;Bawi Khrih le Khrihfabu caah&quot; tiin, Porhhlawt, ruamkainak le mah zawn
 lawng ruahnak zong, Kan hlawt tikah kan Bawipa orhlei kam ah, Lunglawm in
 kan thu cio lai, dong ti loin.

[C4]
   Jesuh kan Khamhbawi ca le, A thi in a cawkmi, Amah a Khrihfabu
   ca-ah, Bawipa kan thianter ko.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
</song>